<center>
  <!DOCTYPE html>
  <html lang="en" dir="ltr">

  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Calculate your Income Tax</title>

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/style2.css">
    <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.5.1/jquery.min.js"></script>

  </head>

  <body>
    <div>
      <a style="color: antiquewhite; text-decoration: none; " href="/">TAX MANAGEMENT SYSTEM</a>
      <% if(user) { %>
        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-outline-success m-1"
          style="width:10%;height:40px; position: relative; left:400px;"><a href="/logout"
            style="text-decoration: none;">LogOut</a></button>
        <% } else { %>
          <button type="submit" class="btn btn-outline-success m-1"
            style="width:10%;height:40px;  position: relative; left:400px;"><a href="/login"
              style="text-decoration: none;"> Login</a></button>
          <% } %>
          <button type="submit" class="btn btn-outline-success m-1"
            style="width:10%;height:40px;"><a href="/history"
              style="text-decoration: none;"> History</a></button>
    </div>
    <div style="background-image: url('images/tax_c.jpg'); width:100%;">
      <h1 style="text-align:center;"> INCOME TAX CALCULATOR </h1>
      <p>The rules followed in evaluating the amount can be read in detail <a
          href="https://cleartax.in/s/income-tax">here.</a></p>
      <form action="/main" method="post">
        <label>
          <h2 style="font-size:200%;">Your income </h2>
        </label>
        <br></br>
        <input type="number" min="0" id="income" name="income" placeholder=" Enter your income" />
        <br></br>
        <label>
          <h2 style="font-size:200%;">Are you a salaried employee?</h2>
        </label>
        <input type="checkbox" name = "salaried" value="YES" />
        <label for="Income"> YES </label><br>
        <br></br>
        <input type="checkbox" name = "notSalaried" value="NO">
        <label for="Income"> NO </label><br>
        <label>
          <h2 style="font-size:200%;">Deduction under section 80C</h2>
        </label>
        <p> It allows a maximum deduction of Rs 1.5 lakh every year from the taxpayers total income.
          The benefit of this deduction can be availed by Individuals and HUFs. Companies, partnership firms, LLPs
          cannot avail the benefit of this deduction. Read more about it <a
            href="https://cleartax.in/s/80c-80-deductions">here.</a></p>
        <input type="number" min="0" max="12500" id="deductionC" name="deductionC"
          placeholder=" Your contribution to National Pension System and other expenses...(" NPS"). Deductions upto
          12,500" />
        <label>
          <h2 style="font-size:200%;">Deduction under section 80D</h2>
        </label>
        <p>Every individual or HUF can claim a deduction from their total income under section 80D for medical insurance
          premium paid in any given year.Read more about it <a href="https://cleartax.in/s/medical-insurance">here.</a>
        </p>
        <input type="number" min="0" max="2084" id="deductionD" name="deductionD" placeholder="INCLUDES: health insurance
  Max deduction â‚¹2084" />
        <label>
          <h2 style="font-size:200%;">Deduction under Section 80E</h2>
        </label>
        <p>The loan should be taken for the higher education of self, spouse or children or for a student for whom the
          individual is a legal guardian. Read more about it <a
            href="https://cleartax.in/s/section-80e-deduction-interest-education-loan">here</a></p>
        <input type="number" min="0" id="deductionE" name="deductionE"
          placeholder="Interest paid on education loan. No limit on Maximum deduction" />
        <label>
          <h2 style="font-size:200%;">Other deductions</h2>
        </label>
        <p>Read more about it <a href="https://cleartax.in/s/income-tax">here</a></p>
        <input type="number" id="otherDeductions" name="otherDeductions" placeholder="Enter amount" />
        <br>
        <button type="submit"> Submit and Calculate</button>
      </form>
      <br>
      <label>
        <h2 style="font-size:200%;">Your Income Tax is :</h2>
      </label>
      <br></br>
      <p>
        Tax under option 1, with all deductions
      </p>
      <input type=text id=tax name=tax placeholder="<%= tax1 %>" readonly />
      <script src=https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.11.3/jquery.min.js></script>
      <script src=https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.5/js/bootstrap.min.js></script>

      <script>$(document).ready(function () { $("#submit").click(function () { var a = 0; var b = $("#income").val(); if (b <= 250000) { a = 0 } if (b > 250000 && b <= 500000) { a = (b - 250000) * 10 / 100 } if (b > 500000 && b <= 1000000) { a = 25000 + ((b - 500000) * 20 / 100) } if (b > 1000000) { a = (25000 + 100000) + ((b - 1000000) * 30 / 100) } $("#tax").val(a) }) });</script>

      <br></br>
      <p>Tax under Section 115BAC(different slab rates and no deductions). Read more about it <a
          href="https://cleartax.in/s/section-115bac-features-new-tax-regime-benefits">here.</a></p>
      <input type=text id=tax name=tax placeholder="<%= tax2 %>" readonly />
      <script src=https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.11.3/jquery.min.js></script>
      <script src=https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.5/js/bootstrap.min.js></script>
      <script>$(document).ready(function () { $("#submit").click(function () { var a = 0; var b = $("#income").val(); if (b <= 250000) { a = 0 } if (b > 250000 && b <= 500000) { a = (b - 250000) * 10 / 100 } if (b > 500000 && b <= 1000000) { a = 25000 + ((b - 500000) * 20 / 100) } if (b > 1000000) { a = (25000 + 100000) + ((b - 1000000) * 30 / 100) } $("#tax").val(a) }) });</script>
      <p>Lowest among the two is:</p>
      <input type=text id=tax name=tax placeholder="<%= minTax %>" readonly />
      <script src=https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.11.3/jquery.min.js></script>
      <script src=https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.3.5/js/bootstrap.min.js></script>

      <script>$(document).ready(function () { $("#submit").click(function () { var a = 0; var b = $("#income").val(); if (b <= 250000) { a = 0 } if (b > 250000 && b <= 500000) { a = (b - 250000) * 10 / 100 } if (b > 500000 && b <= 1000000) { a = 25000 + ((b - 500000) * 20 / 100) } if (b > 1000000) { a = (25000 + 100000) + ((b - 1000000) * 30 / 100) } $("#tax").val(a) }) });</script>
  </body>

  </html>